<h1>
  <i class="fas fa-dumbbell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  Welcome to Fitness Tracker: Exercise Menu!
  
</h1>


<h4>
  <i class="fas fa-search-plus text-2xl text-info" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  Create and save a new workout in database. Click on category images for exercise suggestions then store in database...</h4>
<hr class="border-warning">
<p class="font-italic">
  <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <i class="fas fa-chart-bar text-2xl text-warning" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  Save your sets/reps/weights on the spot and monitor progress them in Stats section along with below feature of the app:
</p>
<p class="font-italic">
  <i class="fas fa-info-circle text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <i class="fas fa-award text-2xl text-warning" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  Challenge yourself to complete specific number of workouts in a short-term period, also need to find a reward -to yourself, not by us, by yourself- when the goal achieved...   
</p>

<h2 class="text-primary text-center pb-4"> 
   <i class="infinite animated slideInUp fas fa-dumbbell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  Muscle Builders 
   <i class="infinite animated slideInUp fas fa-dumbbell" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <span class="float-right">
  <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#muscle_div" aria-expanded="false"
      aria-controls="muscle_div"
      id="collapse_muscle_button">
    <span class="collapse_muscle_text"> Show </span>
    <i id="collapse_muscle_icon" class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  </button>
  </span>

  </h2>

<div class="collapse show" id="muscle_div">
  <div class="row">
  {{#each lifting as |lift|}}
    <div class="col-3">
      <btn class="btn btn-block btn-outline-primary rounded-xl w-100 h-100">

          <img class="img-lift" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/attila5287/mongofitness/main/public/img/target_areas/{{lift}}.png" alt="{{lift}}-img">
          
      </btn>
      
        <h4 class="text-center text-uppercase">
          {{lift}}
        </h4>

    </div>
  {{/each}}

  </div>
  
</div>  


<h2 class="text-secondary text-center">
   <i class="infinite animated fadeOutDown fas fa-burn text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
   <i class="infinite animated fadeOutDown fas fa-burn" aria-hidden="true"></i>
   Calorie Burners
   <i class="infinite animated fadeOutDown fas fa-burn text-md" aria-hidden="true"></i>
   <i class="infinite animated fadeOutDown fas fa-burn text-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
     <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary float-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#calorie_div" aria-expanded="false"
         aria-controls="calorie_div" id="collapse_calorie_button">
       <span class="collapse_calorie_text"> Show </span>
       <i id="collapse_calorie_icon" class="fas fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i>
     </button>
</h2>

   <div class="collapse show" id="calorie_div">
  <div class="row">
  {{#each burning as |burn|}}
    <div class="col-3"> 
      <btn class="btn btn-block btn-outline-secondary rounded-xl w-100 h-100">

          <img class="img-burn" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/attila5287/mongofitness/main/public/img/illustration/{{burn}}.png" alt="{{burn}}-img">
          
      </btn>
      
        <h4 class="text-center text-uppercase">
          {{burn}}
        </h4>

    </div>
  {{/each}}


  </div>
     
   </div>
